# StayHealthy 🩺💚

StayHealthy is a modern and user-friendly medical appointment booking web app designed to simplify how patients connect with doctors. With a clean interface, soft colors, and a focus on accessibility, the platform allows users to browse doctors, book appointments, receive notifications, submit reviews, and manage their personal profile — all in one place.

## 🌿 Key Features
- 🧑‍⚕️ Browse doctors and view specialties
- 📅 Book appointments easily online
- 🔔 Get instant notifications and updates
- 🌟 Submit one-time reviews after visits
- 👤 Manage and update your personal profile
- 🔐 Secure login and registration system
- 🙈 Friendly 404 page with a human touch

## 🎨 Design & Theme
The UI uses calming tones like soft sky blue (`#D8ECF3`) and mint green (`#B2E2D0`) with white space and rounded elements for a soothing, professional look. Icons are friendly and clean, such as stethoscopes, calendars, hearts, and bells.

